{"tid":1195023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蔡英文回應香港50萬人示威：一國兩制不是台灣選項","createTime":"2019-06-09T13:34:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T13:40:25.000Z","uid":5195,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"72849675606d7fb1831e593bff49d8ed55f9753d","tid":1195023,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T13:34:54.000Z","msg":"因為對自由的珍視，今天香港50萬人走上街頭，反對被視為「送中惡法」的逃犯條例。<br />\n　　<br />\n我們應該看見的是：香港人民所苦苦追求的人權保障與民主法治，在台灣的土地上卻是如此自然地存在著，這值得我們用心珍惜、用力守護。<br />\n　　<br />\n我們也應該看見，在「一國兩制」之下，短短22年的時間，港人的自由不再理所當然，過去驕傲的現代法制也逐步崩毀。這值得我們深深警醒、深深關切。<br />\n　　<br />\n我們支持所有人對民主自由的追求，也認為香港人民的心聲應被尊重；我們更要大聲向世界說出：台灣人珍愛我們的民主，也堅持我們決定自己命運的權利。「一國兩制」不會是台灣人的選項。<br />\n　　<br />\n照片來源：中央社記者張謙攝<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201906090112.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F201906090112.aspx&d=sUHHPMw%2FtTWAhlV0Ap%2Bq472U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=833873af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201906090112.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"c032e40caa7089e6885cfd4ec8a0b9bac8be4b5d","tid":1195023,"uid":155095,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T13:36:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">台灣人都夠犀利啦</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/1559994004-003bc3b9ecf4a91797becd54120ac7dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2F1559994004-003bc3b9ecf4a91797becd54120ac7dd.jpg&h=01983c09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/1559373045-7d5e34529b39e31dc24bf23272516094.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2F1559373045-7d5e34529b39e31dc24bf23272516094.jpg&h=60f862c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190601/_2019060117062599009.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190601%2F_2019060117062599009.jpg&h=e9dc5bcf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"98b3ec66d19aceb47990132faf79b16248c6a07a","tid":1195023,"uid":26773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T13:38:49.000Z","msg":"比韓生統左台灣既話<br />\n咪又係奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93e54226bc0e4aa25036ec1f5a1e2875e8bf7f5b","tid":1195023,"uid":129340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T13:40:18.000Z","msg":"一國一制 中國原本屬於中華民國 合理"},{"pid":"5df7c6a0ef87d1e15c6740686be5acd2605926ca","tid":1195023,"uid":96453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98b3ec66d19aceb47990132faf79b16248c6a07a","tid":1195023,"uid":26773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T13:38:49.000Z","msg":"比韓生統左台灣既話<br />\n咪又係奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T13:40:25.000Z","msg":"反攻中國大陸，中國民國發大財"}]}